title: Author to give book reading at library
text: Author to give book reading at library Comment Posted Oct. 18, 2015 at 1:00 PM Posted Oct. 18, 2015 at 1:00 PM FREEPORT — Author Cathy Krentz of Darlington, Wisconsin, will give a reading of her newest book at 10:30 a.m. Oct. 21 at the Freeport Public Library, 100 E. Douglas St. The book, “Things That Come in Twos,” is illustrated by Carmen O’Keefe and was inspired by Krentz’s twin granddaughters who entered kindergarten this year. For information: cathykren@yahoo.com.
